  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/e995096ba7d7489215acbd791ce96e84.avif?t=1724823645\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><i>Spot the cards and match the pairs. You only get a short time to memorise so concentration is key. Find the best combos and strategise to hold onto your health and memories. </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/4bc6ead1c19afb2451fe222a7a7f6fc3.poster.avif?t=1724823645\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/4bc6ead1c19afb2451fe222a7a7f6fc3.webm?t=1724823645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/4bc6ead1c19afb2451fe222a7a7f6fc3.mp4?t=1724823645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/f08871e3cd10869e4d99c2e6ae561964.avif?t=1724823645\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><i>Will you choose Clarity, Prudence or Glory? Find your favourite or learn to master all.  </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/c32ed8535017eb8d20b41357e8ebf416.poster.avif?t=1724823645\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/c32ed8535017eb8d20b41357e8ebf416.webm?t=1724823645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/c32ed8535017eb8d20b41357e8ebf416.mp4?t=1724823645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/dd4b43708566c0bb6b20c0915f7f7cd6.avif?t=1724823645\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><i>Unlock achievements and obtain relics to battle your way in Infinite or navigate through the map in Normal or Hard mode.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/ab1f647518ee823ee677775f4ec7111e.poster.avif?t=1724823645\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/ab1f647518ee823ee677775f4ec7111e.webm?t=1724823645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/ab1f647518ee823ee677775f4ec7111e.mp4?t=1724823645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/2922dbc699a24941d8fcf4ceab0da324.avif?t=1724823645\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><i>Hopefully you’ll encounter a friend to help you along the way. </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/5a971c669a42d645042d9831a0bd8e5b.poster.avif?t=1724823645\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/5a971c669a42d645042d9831a0bd8e5b.webm?t=1724823645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021720/extras/5a971c669a42d645042d9831a0bd8e5b.mp4?t=1724823645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
